    "description": "Going Dark is a Stealth Infiltration Game fully coated in the Green Shades of Night Vision.<br><br>You'll be tasked with infiltrating places where any outside communication is either impossible or too dangerous. The only thing you can count on is your own wit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/70f688be199b184fc67460cf0d525164.poster.avif?t=1750518668\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/70f688be199b184fc67460cf0d525164.webm?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/70f688be199b184fc67460cf0d525164.mp4?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Light &amp; Darkness</strong><br>Thanks to your night vision, you can see in the dark, while for the enemies, it's nearly pitch black. You will have to manipulate various sources of light around you in order to succeed on your mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/3412fa6a966817a5151e46d9f9832e2f.poster.avif?t=1750518668\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/3412fa6a966817a5151e46d9f9832e2f.webm?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/3412fa6a966817a5151e46d9f9832e2f.mp4?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Stay out of Sight</strong><br>Go in and out without ever drawing any attention to yourself. Prowl under the cover of darkness and become a master of stealth and infiltration.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/eb41e15ebd45f1f7218af60917ea6132.poster.avif?t=1750518668\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/eb41e15ebd45f1f7218af60917ea6132.webm?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056760/extras/eb41e15ebd45f1f7218af60917ea6132.mp4?t=1750518668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Observe, Plan, and Execute</strong><br>Slow down and think. Every situation you find yourself in has more than one solution.",
